{"word":"G2272 - ἡσύχιος - hēsýchios - hay-soo'-khee-os - Peaceable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἡσύχιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hēsýchios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hay-soo'-khee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Peaceable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அமைதலுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"quiet, tranquil"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of a compound probably of a derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G1476 - ἑδραῖος - hedraîos - hed-rah'-yos/1476\">G1476</a> and perhaps <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; properly <i>keeping</i> one&rsquo;s <i>seat</i> (<i>sedentary</i>), that is, (by implication) <i>still</i> (<i>undisturbed</i>, <i>undisturbing</i>): - peaceable, quiet.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}